<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="gsz0754b29shiHuiNeng"><lb
ed="T" n="0754b29"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0754b29"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000030578">韶州今南華寺</placeName><persName key="A001719">慧能</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0754c01"/><persName key="A001719">釋慧能</persName>，姓盧氏，<placeName key="PL000000031876">南海新興</placeName>人也，其本世居<placeName key="PL000000002485">范<lb
        ed="T" n="0754c02"/>陽</placeName>。厥考諱<persName key="A018985">行瑫</persName>，<date from-iso="0618" key="j19469511950091" to-iso="0627">武德中</date>流<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>亭</sic><corr>于</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz4"/><placeName key="PL000000031875">新州</placeName>百姓<ptr target="#n1311"/>，終於<lb
ed="T" n="0754c03"/>貶所。略述家系，避盧亭<ptr target="#n1310"/>島夷之不敏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1313"/>也。<date from-iso="0638-01-24" key="j19541081954491" to-iso="0639-02-11">貞<lb
ed="T" n="0754c04"/>觀十二年戊戌歲</date>生<persName key="A001719">能</persName>也，純淑迂懷，惠性間<lb
ed="T" n="0754c05"/>出。雖蠻風獠俗，漬染不深，而詭行么形<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1315"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>駁<lb
ed="T" n="0754c06"/>維</sic><corr>駮<lb
        ed="T" n="0754c06"/>雜</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz5"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1314"/>難測。父既少失，母<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz6"/>且<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz6"/>寡居，家亦屢空，業無<lb
ed="T" n="0754c07"/>腴產。<persName key="A001719">能</persName>負薪矣，日售荷擔。偶聞𨞬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g640"/>肆間誦<lb
ed="T" n="0754c08"/>《金剛般若經》，<persName key="A001719">能</persName>凝神屬垣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1316"/>，遲遲不去，問曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0754c09"/>「誰邊受學此經？」曰：「從<placeName key="PL000000028109">蘄州黃梅馮茂山</placeName><persName key="A000237">忍<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0754c10"/>師</roleName></persName>勸持此法，云即得見性成佛也。」<persName key="A001719">能</persName>聞是<lb
ed="T" n="0754c11"/>說。若渴夫之飲寒漿也，忙歸，備所須留奉<lb
ed="T" n="0754c12"/>親老。<date from-iso="0670" key="j19658611967498" to-iso="0674">咸亨</date>中，往<placeName key="PL000000030617">韶陽</placeName>，遇<persName key="A010062">劉志略</persName>。<persName key="A010062">略</persName>有姑<persName key="A018986">無<lb
ed="T" n="0754c13"/>盡藏</persName>，恒讀《涅槃經》。<persName key="A001719">能</persName>聽之，即為<ref type="person" target="#A018986">尼</ref>辨析中<lb
ed="T" n="0754c14"/>義。怪<persName key="A001719">能</persName>不識文字，乃曰：「諸佛理論，若取文<lb
ed="T" n="0754c15"/>字，非佛意也。」<ref type="person" target="#A018986">尼</ref>深歎服，號為<ref type="person" target="#A001719">行者</ref><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1317"/>。有勸<lb
ed="T" n="0754c16"/>於<placeName key="PL000000030578">寶林古寺</placeName>修道，自謂<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz7"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz7"/>曰：「本誓求師，而<lb
ed="T" n="0754c17"/>貪住寺取乎道也，何異却行歸舍乎？」明日<lb
ed="T" n="0754c18"/>遂行，至<placeName key="PL000000030688">樂昌縣</placeName>西石窟，依附<persName key="A010063">智遠<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，侍座<lb
ed="T" n="0754c19"/>談玄。<persName key="A010063">遠</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A001719">行者</ref>迨非凡常之見龍，<ref type="person" target="#A010063">吾</ref>不知，<lb
ed="T" n="0754c20"/><ref type="person" target="#A010063">吾</ref>不知之甚矣！」勸往<placeName key="PL000000028083">蘄春</placeName><ref type="person" target="#A000237">五祖</ref>所印證去，<lb
ed="T" n="0754c21"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A010063">吾</ref>終於下風<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1108"/>請教也。」未幾造<ref type="person" target="#A000237">焉</ref>，<persName key="A000237">忍<roleName>師</roleName></persName>覩<persName key="A001719">能</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0754c22"/>氣貌不揚，試<ref type="person" target="#A001719">之</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A001719">汝</ref>從何至？」對曰：「<placeName key="PL000000023027">嶺表</placeName>來<lb
ed="T" n="0754c23"/>參<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz8"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz8"/>，唯求作佛。」<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>曰：「<placeName key="PL000000030465">嶺南</placeName>人無佛性。」<persName key="A001719">能</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0754c24"/>「人有南北，佛性無南北。」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A001719">汝</ref>作何功德？」曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0754c25"/>「願竭力抱石而<anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz9"/>舂<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz9"/>，供眾而已。」如是勞乎井<lb
ed="T" n="0754c26"/><anchor xml:id="beg0754sgsz10"/>臼<anchor xml:id="end0754sgsz10"/>，率淨人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g695"/>而在先；了彼死生，與涅槃而平<lb
ed="T" n="0754c27"/>等。<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>雖均養，心何辨知？俾<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>唱予，致<persName key="A001719">能</persName>和<lb
ed="T" n="0754c28"/>汝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1026"/>。偈辭在壁，見解分岐，揭厲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1031"/>不同，淺深斯<lb
ed="T" n="0754c29"/>別<ptr target="#n1312"/>。<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>密以法衣寄託曰：「古我先師轉相付<pb ed="T" n="0755a" xml:id="T50.2061.0755a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0755a01"/>授，豈徒爾哉。嗚呼！後世受<ref type="person" target="#A000237">吾</ref>衣者命若懸<lb
ed="T" n="0755a02"/>絲，<ref type="person" target="#A001719">小子</ref>識之。」<persName key="A001719">能</persName>計迴<ref type="place" target="#PL000000031876">生地</ref>，隱於<placeName key="PL000000031242">四會</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000031146">懷集</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0755a03"/>之間，漸露鋒頴。就<placeName key="PL000000030463">南海</placeName><persName key="A009251">印宗<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>《涅槃》盛<lb
ed="T" n="0755a04"/>集，論風旛之語，<persName key="A009251">印宗</persName>辭屈而神伏，乃為<ref type="person" target="#A001719">其</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0755a05"/>削椎髻於<placeName key="PL000000030435">法性寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1313"/>，<persName key="A007208">智光律師</persName>邊受滿分戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0755a06"/>所登之壇即<date from-iso="0420" key="j18746541896160" to-iso="0479">南宋朝</date><persName key="A000218">求那跋摩<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>之所築<lb
ed="T" n="0755a07"/>也。<persName key="A000218">跋摩</persName>已登果位，懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>云：「後當有肉身菩<lb
ed="T" n="0755a08"/>薩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1318"/>於斯受戒。」又<date from-iso="0543" key="j19197471924818" to-iso="0557">梁末</date><persName key="A000962">真諦三藏</persName>於壇之畔<lb
ed="T" n="0755a09"/>手植菩提樹，謂眾曰：「種此後一百二十年，<lb
ed="T" n="0755a10"/>有開士<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1319"/>於其下說無上乘，度無量眾。」至<lb
ed="T" n="0755a11"/>是<persName key="A001719">能</persName>爰宅于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000030435">茲</ref>，果於樹陰開<placeName key="PL000000028112">東山</placeName>法門，皆<lb
ed="T" n="0755a12"/>符前讖也。<date from-iso="0674" key="j19674991968318" to-iso="0676">上元</date>中，正演暢宗風，慘然不悅。<lb
ed="T" n="0755a13"/>大眾問曰：「胡無情緒耶？」曰：「遷流不息，生滅<lb
ed="T" n="0755a14"/>無常，<ref type="person" target="#A000237">吾師</ref>今歸寂矣！」凶赴至而信。乃移住<placeName key="PL000000030578">寶<lb
ed="T" n="0755a15"/>林寺</placeName>焉。時刺史<persName key="A010065">韋據</persName>命出<placeName key="PL000000030559">大梵寺</placeName>，苦辭，入<lb
ed="T" n="0755a16"/><placeName key="PL000000030577">雙峯曹侯溪</placeName>矣。大龍倏起，飛雨澤以均施，<lb
ed="T" n="0755a17"/>品物攸滋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1320"/>，逐根荄而受益<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1321"/>。五納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1322"/>之客擁塞<lb
ed="T" n="0755a18"/>于門，四部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>之賓圍繞其座。時宣祕偈，或舉<lb
ed="T" n="0755a19"/>契經<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1122"/>，一切普熏，咸聞象藏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1323"/>；一時登富，悉握蛇<lb
ed="T" n="0755a20"/>珠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1324"/>；皆由徑途，盡歸圓極，所以天下言禪<lb
ed="T" n="0755a21"/>道者以<placeName key="PL000000030577">曹溪</placeName>為口實<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1325"/>矣。洎乎九重下聽，<lb
ed="T" n="0755a22"/>萬里懸心，思布露而奉迎<ptr target="#n1304"/>，欲歸依而適願。<lb
ed="T" n="0755a23"/><persName key="A002099">武太后</persName>、<persName key="A002100">孝和皇帝</persName>咸降璽書，詔赴<placeName key="PL000000042189">京闕</placeName>，蓋<lb
ed="T" n="0755a24"/><persName key="A009582">神秀<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>之奏舉也。續遣中官<ptr type="glossary" target="#g932"/><persName key="A010066">薛簡</persName>往詔，<lb
ed="T" n="0755a25"/>復謝病不起。<persName key="A018990">子牟</persName>之心敢忘鳳闕，<persName key="A001204">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0755a26"/>足不過<placeName key="PL000000018788">虎溪</placeName>，固以此辭，非邀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1326"/>君也。遂賜<lb
ed="T" n="0755a27"/>摩納袈裟<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1327"/>一緣、鉢一口、編珠織成經巾、綠質<lb
ed="T" n="0755a28"/>紅暈花綿巾、絹五百匹，充供養云<ptr target="#n1315"/>。又捨<placeName key="PL000000031876">新<lb
ed="T" n="0755a29"/>興</placeName>舊宅為<placeName key="PL000000031861">國恩寺</placeName>焉。<date from-iso="0707-02-11" key="j19793271979566" to-iso="0707-10-08">神龍三年</date>，勅<placeName key="PL000000030551">韶州</placeName>可<pb ed="T" n="0755b" xml:id="T50.2061.0755b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0755b01"/>修<persName key="A001719">能</persName>所居寺佛殿并方丈，務從嚴飾，賜改<lb
ed="T" n="0755b02"/>額曰<placeName key="PL000000030578">法泉</placeName>也。<date from-iso="0712-08-11" key="j19813351981364" to-iso="0712-09-09">延和元年七月</date>，命弟子於<placeName key="PL000000031861">國<lb
ed="T" n="0755b03"/>恩寺</placeName>建浮圖一所，促令速就。以<date key="j19817211981721" when-iso="0713-09-01">先天二年<lb
ed="T" n="0755b04"/>八月三日</date>俄然示疾，異香滿室，白虹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1328"/>屬地<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1329"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0755b05"/>飯食訖，沐浴更衣，彈指<ptr type="glossary" target="#g507"/>不絕，氣微目瞑，全身<lb
ed="T" n="0755b06"/>永謝。爾時山石傾墮，川源息枯，鳥連韻以哀<lb
ed="T" n="0755b07"/>啼，猿斷腸而叫咽。或唱言曰：「世間眼滅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1330"/>，吾疇<lb
ed="T" n="0755b08"/>依乎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1331"/>！」春秋七十六矣，以<date from-iso="0713-11-27" key="j19818081981836" to-iso="0713-12-25">其年十一月</date>遷座<lb
ed="T" n="0755b09"/>于<placeName key="PL000000030577">曹溪</placeName>之原也。弟子<persName key="A005612">神會</persName>若<persName key="A002780">顏子</persName>之於<persName key="A002174">孔</persName>門<lb
ed="T" n="0755b10"/>也，勤勤付囑，語在〈<persName key="A005612">會</persName>傳〉。<persName key="A005612">會</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000023656">洛陽荷澤寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0755b11"/>崇樹<persName key="A001719">能</persName>之真堂。兵部侍郎<persName key="A010068">宋鼎</persName>為碑焉。<persName key="A005612">會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0755b12"/>序宗脈，從<persName key="A002799">如來</persName>下<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>諸祖外，<placeName key="PL000000000083">震旦</placeName>凡<persName key="G000017">六<lb
ed="T" n="0755b13"/>祖</persName>，盡圖繢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g794"/>其影。太尉<persName key="A010069">房琯</persName>作《六葉圖序》。又<lb
ed="T" n="0755b14"/>以<persName key="A001719">能</persName>端形不散，如入禪定，後加漆布矣。復<lb
ed="T" n="0755b15"/>次<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>僧<persName key="A010070">方辯</persName>塑小樣真，肖同疇昔。<persName key="A001719">能</persName>曾言：<lb
ed="T" n="0755b16"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A001719">吾</ref>滅後有善心男子必取<ref type="person" target="#A001719">吾</ref>元<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1332"/>，汝曹勿怪。」<lb
ed="T" n="0755b17"/>或憶是言，加鐵環纏頸焉。<date from-iso="0723-02-14" key="j19851741985528" to-iso="0724-02-03">開元十一年</date>，果<lb
ed="T" n="0755b18"/>有<placeName key="PL000000024045">汝州</placeName>人受<placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅</placeName>客購，潛施刃<ref type="person" target="#A001719">其</ref>元，欲凾<lb
ed="T" n="0755b19"/>歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000048606">海東</ref>供養。有聞擊鐵聲而擒之。其塔<lb
ed="T" n="0755b20"/>下葆藏屈眴布<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1333"/>欝多羅僧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1334"/>，其色青黑，碧縑複<lb
ed="T" n="0755b21"/>袷，非人間所有物也。屢經盜去，迷倒却行<lb
ed="T" n="0755b22"/>而還褫之。<date from-iso="0756" key="j19974111997993" to-iso="0758">至德</date>中，<persName key="A005612">神會</persName>遣弟子<persName key="A010072">進平</persName>送牙<lb
ed="T" n="0755b23"/>癢和<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1335"/>一柄。朝達名公所重，有若<persName key="A011689">宋之問</persName>謁<lb
ed="T" n="0755b24"/><persName key="A001719">能</persName>，著長篇<ptr target="#n1316"/>。有若<persName key="A002473">張<roleName>燕公</roleName>說</persName>寄香十斤并詩，<lb
ed="T" n="0755b25"/>附<persName key="A009217">武平一</persName>至，詩云：「<ref type="person" target="#A001719">大師</ref>捐世去，空留法身<lb
ed="T" n="0755b26"/>在！願寄無礙香，隨心到<placeName key="PL000000030463">南海</placeName>。」<persName key="A009217">武<roleName>公</roleName></persName>因門人<lb
ed="T" n="0755b27"/><persName key="A004015">懷讓</persName>鑄巨鐘，為撰銘讚，<persName key="A011689">宋之問</persName>書。次<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣州</placeName><lb
        ed="T" n="0755b28"/>節度<persName key="A010074">宋璟</persName>來<anchor xml:id="beg0755sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0755sgsz1"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000030579">其塔</ref>。問弟子<persName key="A016638">令韜</persName>無生法忍<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1336"/><lb
ed="T" n="0755b29"/>義。<persName key="A010074">宋<roleName>公</roleName></persName>聞法歡喜，向<ref type="place" target="#PL000000030579">塔</ref>乞示徵祥。須臾，微<pb ed="T" n="0755c" xml:id="T50.2061.0755c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0755c01"/>風漸起，異香裛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1051"/>人，陰雨霏霏，只周一寺耳。<lb
ed="T" n="0755c02"/>稍多奇瑞，逭繁不錄。後<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>下詔<persName key="A001719">能</persName>弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0755c03"/><persName key="A016638">令韜</persName>，<persName key="A016638">韜</persName>稱疾不赴，遣<persName key="A018993">明象</persName>齎傳法衣鉢進<lb
ed="T" n="0755c04"/>呈畢，給還。<persName key="A002120">憲宗皇帝</persName>追諡曰<persName key="A001719">大鑒</persName>，塔曰<placeName key="PL000000030579">元和<lb
ed="T" n="0755c05"/>正真</placeName>也。迨<anchor xml:id="beg0755sgsz2"/>夫<anchor xml:id="end0755sgsz2"/><date from-iso="0835-03-10" key="j20261062052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐季</date><ref type="person" target="#A006590 #A006591 #A006592 #A006593">劉氏</ref>稱制<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>，每遇上<lb
ed="T" n="0755c06"/>元燒燈<ptr target="#n1318"/>，迎真身入城，為民祈福。<placeName key="PL000000000107">大宋</placeName>平<lb
ed="T" n="0755c07"/><placeName key="PL000000030459">南海</placeName>後，<placeName key="PL000000030569">韶州</placeName>盜<persName key="A010076">周思瓊</persName>叛換<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1337"/>，盡焚其寺塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0755c08"/>將延燎。平時肉身，非數夫莫舉。煙熛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1338"/>向逼，<lb
ed="T" n="0755c09"/>二僧對舁，輕如夾紵像焉。<date from-iso="0978-02-15" key="j20783132078667" to-iso="0979-02-04">太平興國三年</date>，<ref type="person" target="#A001640">今<lb
ed="T" n="0755c10"/>上</ref>勅重建塔，改為<placeName key="PL000000030578">南華寺</placeName>矣。</p>
<p><lb
ed="T" n="0755c11"/>系曰：「<persName key="A000237">五祖</persName>自何而識一介白衣，便付衣耶？」<lb
ed="T" n="0755c12"/>通曰：「一言知心，更無疑貳。況復記心輪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1339"/>間<lb
ed="T" n="0755c13"/>如指之掌。」<persName key="A000237">忍<roleName>師</roleName></persName>施<anchor xml:id="beg0755sgsz3"/>一味<anchor xml:id="end0755sgsz3"/>法，何以在家受衣<lb
ed="T" n="0755c14"/>鉢乎？<persName key="A009582">秀<roleName>師</roleName></persName>則否。通曰：「是法寧選緇白？得者<lb
ed="T" n="0755c15"/>則傳。周封諸侯，乃分分器<ptr type="glossary" target="#g176"/>，同姓異姓別也。<lb
ed="T" n="0755c16"/>以祖師甄別精麁，以衣為信。譬如三力士<lb
ed="T" n="0755c17"/>射堅洛叉<ptr target="#n1317"/>，一<persName key="A018997">摩健那</persName>射則中而不破；二<persName key="A018998">鉢羅<lb
ed="T" n="0755c18"/>塞建提</persName>破而不度；三<persName key="A018994">那羅延</persName>箭度而復穿餘<lb
ed="T" n="0755c19"/>物也。非堅洛叉有強弱，但由射勢力不同<lb
ed="T" n="0755c20"/>耳。<persName key="A001719"><roleName>南</roleName>能</persName>可謂<persName key="A018994">那羅延</persName>射而獲賞焉。」信衣至<lb
ed="T" n="0755c21"/><persName key="A001719">能</persName>不傳，莫同<persName key="A002761">夏禹</persName>之家天下乎？通曰：「<persName key="A000237">忍</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0755c22"/>言受傳衣者，命若懸絲，如是<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>之意也。又<lb
ed="T" n="0755c23"/><persName key="A005612">會</persName>也稟祖法則有餘，行化行則不足。故<lb
ed="T" n="0755c24"/>後致<placeName key="PL000000026800">均部</placeName>之流<ptr target="#n1319"/>，方驗<persName key="A001719">能<roleName>師</roleName></persName>之先覺，不傳無<lb
ed="T" n="0755c25"/>私悋之咎矣。故曰知人則哲也，吁！」</p>
